high_descs: Turn left, go to the ottoman, go around the back side of the coffee table near the wall, turn to face the remote on the coffee table.
Pick up the remote on the coffee table.
Bring the remote to the right to the lamp in the corner, behind the chair, go around the left side of the chair to get to the lamp.
Turn on the tall lamp in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Examine a remote in the light of the tall lamp.

high_descs: Head forward and take a left at the stairs, go past the ottoman, take a right and then a quick right to face the coffee table in front of the couch
Pick up the remote control that is sitting on the coffee table
Turn right, then take a left at the ottoman, then right after you pass the chair, another quick right to go around the chair then walk to the tall floor lamp
Turn on the tall floor lamp
anns.task_desc: Examine a remote control under a tall lamp

high_descs: Walk forward a few steps, turn left, walk to the ottoman, turn right, turn left to walk between the ottoman and coffee table, walk to the wall, turn right, then turn right again to face the coffee table.
Pick up the remote control that is on the coffee table.
Turn right, walk forward, making a left to walk between the coffee table and ottoman, turn right, walk forward, then turn right to walk up to the floor lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a remote control using the light of a floor lamp.
